## Buck targets

- `//projects/libs/{{ name }}:{{ name }}` — Node library (stamp)
- `//projects/libs/{{ name }}:copy_addon` — copies the `.node` artifact to `native/{{ addon_name }}.node`
- `//projects/libs/{{ name }}-native:napi_addon` — C++ addon that produces the `.node` artifact

